&lt;h5 id=&#34;adaptation-for-link-prediction&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#adaptation-for-link-prediction&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Adaptation for Link Prediction.&lt;/h5&gt;
